<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-xl-8">
            <div class="section_title mb-20 text-center">
                <h3 style="margin-top:30px;">
                    Backyard
                </h3>
                <hr />
                <p style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:30px;">
                    This is an ordinary life scene, a small backyard.
                    There are some garbage generated in our lives here.
                    We can also compost in our backyard.
                    You can click on different parts of the scene to get related information.<br />
                    You can click on the <a href="#Map" class="btn-link" style="color:#12b322; font-size:18px;"><strong>map</strong></a> function to find more data about garbage collection according to the area you live in, such as checking the time of garbage collection, the website of the council.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
